<item>
            <title>[PDFBOX-970] TeX-created ligatures and umlauts are not recognised</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PDFBOX-970</link>
                <project id="12310760" key="PDFBOX">PDFBox</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Ligatures in a TeX-created document are lost, which are regognised by v. 1.4, e.g.&lt;br/&gt;
  1.4		 1.5&lt;br/&gt;
official	ocial&lt;br/&gt;
effort 	e ort&lt;br/&gt;
fields 	elds&lt;br/&gt;
first	         rst&lt;br/&gt;
In addition, German umlauts (&#228;, &#246;, &#252;) are represented as ( a,  o,  u), &lt;/p&gt;</description>
